FBIS4-28908 "dreas114_c_94001" FBIS-EAS-94-114 Daily Report 10 Jun 1994 North Korea `Massive' Combined `War Exercise' Reported `Massive' Combined `War Exercise' Reported SK1006051394 Pyongyang KCNA in English 0456 GMT 10 Jun 94 SK1006051394 Pyongyang KCNA English BFN [Text] Pyongyang, June 10 (KCNA) -- The South Korean war-thirsty elements on June 9 staged a massive combined air-ground-sea war exercise against the North in the southern area of East Coast by mobilizing destroyers, Naval planes and Airforce planes of the puppet Army, according to a radio report from Seoul. The drill for "increasing the capacity of combined operations" shows that the puppets are running [words indistinct] the train of war against the North, taking issue with the fictitious "nuclear issue" of the North.
